Paro mag fuwo


1  Kaka lwang’ni motho nyalo ketho mo mang’ue ng’ar mi dum tik marach, e kaka fuwo matin nono bende nyalo ketho rieko maduong’.


2  Pile ng’at mariek timo atima gik makare. Ng’at mofuwo to timo mana gik maricho. 
3  Fupe nenore anena kata mana kowuotho e yo, omiyo ji duto ng’eyo ni en ng’at mofuwo.


4  Ka ruoth okecho kodi, to kik iwe tich mitiyone, nikech ka ibolori, to onyalo ng’wononi kata mana ketho madongo.


5  Koro nitie gima rach ma aseneno ka ruodhi timo e piny ka. 
6  Giketo joma ofuwo e tije madongo. Joma omew to ok gidew. 
7  Bende aseneno ka wasumbni oidho farese, to jodongo wuotho gi tiendgi ka wasumbni.


8  

Ka ikunyo bur, to in ema inyumorie, kata ka ipowo kor ot, to in ema thuol kayi. 
9  Ka ikunyo kite, to kite nyaka hinyi, kendo ka ibaro yien, to nyaka ihinyri kibero. 
10  Ka ng’ato tong’o gi le modik, ma ok opiago, to nyaka oti kode gi muya, eka otong’ gimoro. Kuom mano, ber chano gik moko mokwongo ka pok itimo. 
11  Ka thuol okayi ka pok iboye, to onge ohala ma iyudo kuom ng’eyo boyo thuonde!


12  Weche ma ng’at mariek wacho, kelone luor. Ng’at mofuwo to tiekore kende owuon gi wechene. 
13  Ochako wuoyo gi weche mofuwo, to otieko gi weche maricho mag neko, 
14  kendo owuoyo awuoya ma ok oling’!

Onge ng’at ma ong’eyo gima biro timore kiny. Kose ere ng’ama nyalo nyisowa gima biro timore bang’ thowa?


15  Joma ofuwo negore gi tich nikech gionge kata mana rieko ma ginyalo ng’eyogo yo ma didwokgi dala.


16  Ka ruodh piny en ng’at ma yolo, kendo jotende galore agala e sewni otieno duto, to pinyno nigi chandruok. 
17  To piny ma ruodhe tiyo gi parone owuon, bende ma jotende timo sewni mana e seche mowinjore, kendo ritore ma ok mer, ema nigi hawi.


18  Ka ng’ato nyap, ma ok nyal umo tat ode, to nyaka ot chuer, mi podhi.


19  Chiemo mabeyo miyo ng’ato bedo mamor, kendo kong’o bende miyo ng’ato winjo maber, to gigo ok yudre ka pesa onge!


20  Kik ikuong’ ruoth kata mana e chunyi. Bende kik iwuo marach kuom jomwandu kata mana ka in kendi e odi mar nindo, nimar dipo ka winyo okawo wachno, motero oko.

